                  </hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">re-examined.</hi> The coat I saw Bennett in was a blue rough pilot coat, at a quarter before five o'clock, and they went towards Wapping—it seemed to be rather a full sized coat—Ward had on a white smock frock.</p>
