                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable R</hi> 23.) I produce a certificate of Bennett's former conviction at this Court—(<hi rend="italic">read Convicted</hi> 17<hi rend="italic">th Dec.</hi>, 1838, <hi rend="italic">having been before convicted, and transported for seven years</hi>)—he is the man.</p>
